&lt;p&gt;原文: &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9tZWRpdW0uY29tL2RhaWx5anMvaS1uZXZlci11bmRlcnN0b29kLWphdmFzY3JpcHQtY2xvc3VyZXMtOTY2MzcwMzM2OGU4&#34;&gt;I never understood JavaScript closures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
